Title: Beginning Impositions
Description:
Darkest greetings, $r. Ahem, yes. Yes! Darkest greetings indeed.

<The lanky man seems to suddenly remember where he is.>

On behalf of my patron, I bid you travel to the Darkmoon Faire. The Faire! Who doesn't love it? Yes. Yes!

Ahem.

She requires your presence, she does! Our Lady of the Midnight Moon. The Damsel of Darkness! The Mother of Crows...

...Madam Shadow.

Objectives.Text: Take Madam Shadow's Stagecoach to the Darkmoon Faire
